#. Tag: title
#: usermanual.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &partman;"
msgstr "Uporaba &partman;"

#. Tag: title
#: usermanual.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the main view showing the currently selected device in a graphical "
"and a tree view, &partman; uses &Qt;'s <quote>dock widgets</quote> or panels "
"to display some information and allow selections. See the following screen "
"shot for an overview of &partman;'s main window."
msgstr ""
"Poleg glavnega pogleda, ki prikazuje trenutno izbrano napravo v grafičnem in "
"drevesnem pogledu, &partman; uporablja <quote>pripomočke</quote> ali plošče "
"&Qt; za prikaz nekaterih informacij in omogoča izbire. Oglejte si naslednji "
"posnetek zaslona za pregled glavnega okna &partman;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: usermanual.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "&partman;'s main window"
msgstr "&partman; glavno okno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: usermanual.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Menubar: The menu bar presents some custom and some non-standard menus to "
"choose actions to perform. All commands are described in detail in <xref "
"linkend=\"reference\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica menija: Menijska vrstica predstavlja nekaj menijev po meri in nekaj "
"nestandardnih menijev za izbiro dejanj za izvedbo. Vsi ukazi so podrobno "
"opisani v <xref linkend=\"reference\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toolbar: &partman;'s tool bar is a standard tool bar. It can be fully "
"customized; for details see <xref linkend=\"menu-settings-help\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica: orodna vrstica &partman; je standardna orodna vrstica. Lahko "
"se popolnoma prilagodi; za podrobnosti glejte <xref linkend=\"menu-settings-"
"help\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Devices Panel: This panel lists all <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-device"
"\">devices</glossterm> found on your computer that &partman; can handle. "
"Select a device in this panel to view or modify it in the graphical device "
"view or in the tree device view."
msgstr ""
"Plošča z napravami: na tej plošči so navedene vse <glossterm linkend="
"\"glossary-device\">naprave</glossterm>, najdene v vašem računalniku, ki jih "
"&partman; nadzira. Izberite napravo na tej plošči, da si jo ogledate ali "
"spremenite v grafičnem pogledu naprav ali v drevesnem pogledu naprav."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Graphical Device View: In this view &partman; shows a graphical "
"representation of the currently selected device. Each of the device's "
"<glossterm linkend=\"glossary-partition\">partitions</glossterm> has its own "
"box with device node name (<quote>sda1</quote> for the first partition in "
"the screenshot above) and usage information (the dark violet area in the "
"screenshot)."
msgstr ""
"Grafični pogled naprave: V tem pogledu &partman; prikazuje grafični prikaz "
"trenutno izbrane naprave. Vsaka od <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-partition"
"\">particij</glossterm> naprave ima svoje polje z imenom vozlišča naprave "
"(<quote>sda1</quote> za prvo particijo na zgornjem posnetku zaslona) in "
"informacijami o uporabi (temno vijolično območje na posnetku zaslona)."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<glossterm linkend=\"glossary-extendedpartition\">Extended partitions</"
"glossterm> are visually distinct by their extra border (light green in the "
"screenshot above) around them."
msgstr ""
"<glossterm linkend=\"glossary-extendedpartition\">Razširjene particije</"
"glossterm> se vizualno razlikujejo po dodatni obrobi (svetlo zelena na "
"zgornjem posnetku zaslona) okoli njih."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select a partition by clicking on it in the graphical device view. A "
"double click opens <link linkend=\"menu-partition-properties\">the "
"partition's properties dialog</link>. A right click shows the partition "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Particijo lahko izberete s klikom nanjo v grafičnem pogledu naprave. Dvojni "
"klik odpre <link linkend=\"menu-partition-properties\">pogovorno okno z "
"lastnostmi particije</link>. Desni klik prikaže kontekstni meni particije."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tree Device View: The tree device view shows extended information about each "
"partition on the selected device. The currently selected partition is "
"highlighted. Double-clicking a partition opens <link linkend=\"menu-"
"partition-properties\">the partition's properties dialog</link>. A right "
"click shows the partition context menu."
msgstr ""
"Drevesni pogled naprav: drevesni pogled naprav prikazuje razširjene "
"informacije o vsaki particiji na izbrani napravi. Trenutno izbrana particija "
"je označena. Dvoklik na particijo odpre <link linkend=\"menu-partition-"
"properties\">pogovorno okno z lastnostmi particije</link>. Desni klik "
"prikaže kontekstni meni particije."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information Panel: The information panel shows some details about the "
"currently selected device or partition. It is not enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Informacijska plošča: informacijska plošča prikazuje nekaj podrobnosti o "
"trenutno izbrani napravi ali particiji. Privzeto ni omogočeno."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pending Operations Panel: This panel lists all operations that will be "
"executed once you choose <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-apply\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Plošča s čakajočimi operacijami: na tej plošči so navedene vse operacije, ki "
"bodo izvedene, ko izberete <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-apply\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the screenshot above, one operation is pending: If the user applies the "
"operations now, the <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-filesystem\">file system</"
"glossterm> on /dev/sdb3 will be checked for errors and, if required, "
"repaired."
msgstr ""
"Na zgornjem posnetku zaslona je ena operacija v čakanju: če uporabnik izvede "
"operacije zdaj, bo <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-filesystem\">datotečni "
"sistem</glossterm> na /dev/sdb3 preverjen za napake in po potrebi popravljen."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Statusbar: The status bar shows how many operations are currently pending."
msgstr ""
"Statusna vrstica: Statusna vrstica prikazuje, koliko operacij je trenutno v "
"teku."

#. Tag: para
#: usermanual.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Log Output Panel: This panel shows log information. It is only of secondary "
"importance for non-advanced users and is not enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Izpisna plošča dnevnika: ta plošča prikazuje podatke dnevnika. Za nenapredne "
"uporabnike je le drugotnega pomena in ni privzeto omogočen."

